inspquestion.description: Hooks/Grips/Lashes: check condition and for proper operation
Leveling Devices: check condition and for proper operation
Rope/Pulley: check for damaged rope and pulley
Safety Shoes: check to insure shoes and tread are in good condition
Welds: inspect all welds for cracks or damage
Crimps/Swages: check for looseness, cracking or other conditions
Bolts/Nuts: check to make sure all nuts are tight and threads are not stripped
Rivets: check to make sure both head and crimp are intact on all rivets
All metal components: check for excessive rust or corrosion
Hardware Items: check to insure top iron, hinges, etc, are fully functional
Guides: check for bends, splits, cracks or other defects
Locks: check for bends, splits, cracks or other defects
Steps/Rung Braces: check for bends, splits, cracks or other defects
Steps/Rungs: check for bends, splits, cracks or other defects
Rails: check for bends, splits, cracks or other defects
